          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "chicken broth). To keep potatoes from browning, chop them last and add the to the"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "adf91f4f-877f-4b3c-bcba-06ed53d2b99b",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "top of your freezer bag."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "4e94b4ea-b50a-4e48-b2ba-baa008f2c75f",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "3. Add evaporated milk to a quart-sized plastic freezer bag. Seal, and add to gallonsized bag."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "a7dc8dfe-a89d-4d44-a5fb-2c8e8bfeb7cc",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "4. Remove as much air from the gallon-sized freezer bag as possible, seal, and lay flat"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "10aedea9-478e-4c5e-9f3f-acc4bf7f307d",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "in your freezer."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "7108424b-f226-406f-a5eb-bdc18385bb86",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "COOK"
        },
        {
