          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "1. The night before cooking, move frozen bag to your refrigerator to thaw."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "ea7cff52-4ea6-45b5-9e5b-29613dfada64",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "2. The morning of cooking, pour contents of gallon-sized freezer bag into your"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "6441d0f0-1f5d-469d-a3af-dae2ef30b71a",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "crockpot and add chicken broth. Keep bag of evaporated milk in the refrigerator."
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "038636b2-92be-4971-80df-e76c95faa553",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "3. Cook item in crockpot on \u201clow\u201d setting for 8 hours, or until carrots and potatoes"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "a06b6355-3458-4f1f-ace4-2502083dc1cd",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "are soft. Stir in evaporated milk and leave lid open a crack. Continue to cook 15"
        },
        {
          "ingredient_id": "2a4e124d-447b-4657-9cf9-9f6f4fe88c53",
          "input_qty": null,
          "input_unit_id": null,
          "is_optional": false,
          "note": null,
          "quantity_kind": "unquantified",
          "raw_text": "minutes or until heated through."
        }
